videos.description: Minnesota quarterback Demry Croft keeps it and runs into the end zone from the 3-yard line to extend the Golden Gopher's lead.
videos.headline: Croft uses legs for Minnesota TD

videos.description: Minnesota safety Duke McGhee stuffs Mikale Wilbon on fourth down and P.J. Fleck loves it.
videos.headline: Fleck fired up after Minnesota gets big stop

videos.description: Minnesota quarterback Demry Croft keeps it and breaks for a 73-yard touchdown run to extend the Golden Gophers lead.
videos.headline: Croft uses legs again for 73-yard TD run

videos.description: Kobe McCrary spins his way around defenders in his 11-yard touchdown run to extend the Golden Gophers' lead.
videos.headline: Minnesota extends lead with TD run from McCrary

videos.description: Tanner Lee throws a pass over the middle and Tyler Hoppes hauls it in for a 14-yard touchdown to cut Minnesota's lead.
videos.headline: Lee connects with Hoppes for Nebraska TD

videos.description: Kobe McCrary scores from the 9-yard line to add to Minnesota's lead in the third quarter.
videos.headline: Minnesota's McCrary comes up with 2nd rushing TD

videos.description: Patrick O'Brien connects with Stanley Morgan Jr. for a 21-yard gain that sets up a Nebraska touchdown.
videos.headline: Morgan hauls in 21-yard pass for Cornhuskers
